33
00:03:08,703 --> 00:03:11,423
It relates to the broad patterns of development for that neighborhood.

34
00:03:11,443 --> 00:03:18,025
It's related with strong architectural families and it has important ties with the shipbuilding industry.

35
00:03:18,425 --> 00:03:31,127
